    <div class="row about-text">
        <div class="col-6">
            <h3>Summer Vibes is a leading specialty retailer of summer apparel, footwear and accessories  for young men and women who want to express their individuality through fashion</h3>
        </div>
        <div id="map" class="col-6">
            <h4>You can find us at 250 Bush st</h4>
            <script type='text/javascript' src='https://www.bing.com/api/maps/mapcontrol?key=At7-9tRWGXGM6Bjn6QrQB7slepzLuMPMb3hnoampu99dqTk61ygAGCmbZKIv1dZT&callback=loadMapScenario' async defer></script>
